    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  We enrolled seven individuals with recurrent symptoms following nirmatrelvir-ritonavir treatment. High viral loads (median 6.1 log\n                  <jats:sub>10</jats:sub>\n                  copies/mL) were detected at enrollment and for a median of 17 days after initial diagnosis. Three of seven had culturable virus for up to 16 days after initial diagnosis. No known resistance-associated mutations were identified.\n                </jats:p>",
